{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n<body><p>更新時間：10:06 2026-04-23 HKT<br/>發佈時間：10:06 2026-04-23 HKT</p>\n<p>發佈時間：10:06 2026-04-23 HKT</p><img alt=\"施明喪禮｜李家鼎哀傷送別前妻無法言語 兩子先後抵達獨欠李泳豪太太\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9a66ac301b69aed4e479c5c68648d80b/2026-04/20260423_ent__01_si.png\"/><p>施明的喪禮今日（4月23日）將於大圍寶福紀念館進行大殮儀式，儀式過後靈柩並移往富山火葬場火化。李家鼎與細仔李泳豪於8時10分到場，問李家鼎身體如何？一臉倦容的他指了指喉嚨沒開腔，李泳豪稱：「佢講唔到嘢。」</p><h2>李泳豪太太Agnes未有現身</h2><p>不過李泳豪的太太Agnes未有現身，李家鼎與李泳豪在靈堂外與早已到場的黃夏蕙打招呼並寒暄幾句，約5分鐘後，李泳漢在「保安隊」護送下抵達，李泳漢企定影相後便步入靈，其後太太是嚴佩鈺（Conny）與小朋友先一步進入靈堂，面帶微笑。</p><p></p><img alt=\"李家鼎與李泳豪在靈堂外與黃夏蕙寒暄幾句。\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/961e4af6d51fa9aa1c177bf84d416669/2026-04/001_1_2.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/9dcc3955b33470cbced226972d2a143b/2026-04/002_0_11.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/c780d5eca324cfd170aa3c5ee8d60223/2026-04/003_0_7.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/a7bf7e9833bb992b6826f6fcf0323766/2026-04/4_12_7.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/391bf98abcf8d2286328b833bda3e5cb/2026-04/5_3_7.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/8e649d0604e7025dc2b7ee32ed1e5eb0/2026-04/006_1_5.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/05ebe021e0b490555ac09be2b74ba736/2026-04/007_0_7.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/47a1e2bc81941c5afc2d17a1608aad8b/2026-04/008_1_3.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/9d6281148671edcb6ca1d27ac1be4638/2026-04/009_1_2.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/d843e02a501eb59cfabecc1beff9a13b/2026-04/010_1_1.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/a62f8c23ab54d0d61b6a3b35c832939c/2026-04/011_0_2.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/f6fe5277ea049f4e10c25545b4f68648/2026-04/012_0_0.jpg\"/><img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/0dc84cd2af0ff316b9e707ad0022c24f/2026-04/013_0_0.jpg\"/><p>最Hit</p>\n</body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-23T03:20:50.171028+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":314,"images":14,"source":"星島頭條","fallback":"none"}}